Play tro choi hot piano tiles with Song Tiles Do ta khong do nang Song gio Hong nhan Bac Phan Jack
This is attractive fun game with hot music songs

Song Tiles Do ta khong do nang Song gio Hong nhan Bac Phan Jack is very simple to play: tap or hold while listen to melody of music

Features of tro choi Song Tiles Do ta khong do nang Song gio Hong nhan Bac Phan Jack
- Note piano tiles combine perfect with Viet songs
- Song La mot thang con trai Jack and more than 100 songs

How to play Song Tiles Do ta khong do nang Song gio Hong nhan Bac Phan Jack
When music notes pass the touch area, touch short note or hold long note.
Finish songs with 2 stars to unlock next songs

If any songs in game is your own, please contact us via email.
